  <description>
    <p
        >dsda-doom is a successor of prboom+ with extra tooling for demo recording and playback,
        with a focus on speedrunning and quality of life.</p>
    <p>dsda-doom includes many new features, such as:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Heretic, Hexen, MBF21, Doom-in-Hexen, UDMF, and MAPINFO support</li>
        <li>In-game console and scripting</li>
        <li>Full controller support</li>
        <li>Palette-based opengl renderer</li>
        <li>Debugging features for testing</li>
        <li>Strict mode for speedrunning</li>
        <li>Various quality of life improvements</li>
        <li>Advanced tools for TASing</li>
        <li>Rewind</li>
      </ul>
  </description>
